MM8D/RPI - Growing house controlling and remote monitoring device
-----------------------------------------------------------------

1. About software
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  It is an internal software for MM8D Raspberry Pi based controlling and
monitoring device. You can view actual status with a browser application
and administrate it with SSH client. There is a version of software  for
PC for i386 processor.

Requirements:

  Hardware: Raspberry Pi 3 Model B or PC
  Software: Raspbian OS Lite or Debian GNU/Linux operation system,
            Apache webserver,
            Perl,
            Python3.


2. How to get installer package for my OS?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  Raspbian OS:      mm8d-sw-0.1-armhf.tar.gz
                    mm8d-eec_0.1-1_armhf.deb
                    mm8d-sw_0.1-1_armhf.deb

  Debian GNU/Linux: mm8d-sw-0.1-i386.tar.gz
                    mm8d-eec_0.1-1_i386.deb
                    mm8d-sw_0.1-1_i386.deb

  for both:         mm8d-web_0.1-1_all.deb


b. Download from Github

  $ git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm8drpi-sw.git

c. Download from Debian repository

  set reporitory:
  $ sudo echo "deb http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list
  $ sudo wget -q -O - http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/KEY.gpg | apt-key add -
  $ sudo apt-get update

  install:
  $ sudo apt-get install mm8d-prepare
  $ mm8d-prepare
  $ sudo apt-get install mm8d-sw mm8d-eec mm8d-web

